<div class="container max-w-4xl mx-auto py-24">
  
  <!-- Opening Declaration -->
  <div class="text-center mb-20">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-8">The Bedrock Manifesto</h1>
    <p class="font-serif text-2xl italic text-text-charcoal max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      This project exists for truth, not comfort. We build on the foundation of the apostles and prophets, Christ Jesus himself being the cornerstone.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Affirmations & Rejections Grid -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-24">
    
    <!-- What We Affirm -->
    <div class="bg-white p-10 border-t-4 border-status-success shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-light mb-8">What We Affirm</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-status-success font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong class="block font-serif text-lg mb-1">God’s Sovereignty</strong>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light">He is the potter; we are the clay. He owes us no explanation.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-status-success font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong class="block font-serif text-lg mb-1">The Cost of Obedience</strong>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light">To follow Christ is to die. There is no version of this that is safe.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-status-success font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
          <div>
            <strong class="block font-serif text-lg mb-1">Faith Without Guarantees</strong>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light">We trust Him for who He is, not for what He gives.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- What We Reject -->
    <div class="bg-bg-dark text-white p-10 border-t-4 border-status-error shadow-sm">
      <h3 class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white/50 mb-8">What We Reject</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-status-error font-bold text-xl">✕</span>
          <div>
            <strong class="block font-serif text-lg mb-1">Prosperity Theology</strong>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70">The lie that godliness is a means to financial gain or ease.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-status-error font-bold text-xl">✕</span>
          <div>
            <strong class="block font-serif text-lg mb-1">Therapeutic Deism</strong>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70">Using Scripture merely to feel better about ourselves.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-status-error font-bold text-xl">✕</span>
          <div>
            <strong class="block font-serif text-lg mb-1">Transactional Faith</strong>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70">"If I do X, God must do Y." This is paganism, not Christianity.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- The Cost -->
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center border-t border-border-subtle pt-20 mb-20">
    <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl mb-6">The Cost</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-text-light mb-8">
      We acknowledge that walking this path often involves loss, waiting, silence, and discipline. We do not pretend these are easy, but we testify that they are the furnace where gold is refined.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Audience Filter -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-24">
    <div class="text-center p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded">
      <h4 class="font-serif text-xl mb-4">Who This Is For</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light">Those willing to endure truth, those who value obedience over ease, and those who are tired of a faith that cannot survive the weight of reality.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded">
      <h4 class="font-serif text-xl mb-4">Who This Is Not For</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light">Those seeking affirmation without change, those demanding certainty before trust, and those looking for a "hack" to spiritual maturity.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Closing -->
  <div class="text-center">
    <p class="font-serif text-xl italic text-text-charcoal">
      Let truth stand on its own.
    </p>
  </div>

</div>
